{"id":183534,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011927/","date":"2011-09-27T23:30:32Z","modified":"2011-09-27T23:30:32Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/9/27","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a> <b>(</b></span><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/yigroup\">@yigroup</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/xiaomi2020\">@xiaomi2020</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/09/27/us-shanghai-trains-idUSTRE78Q0ZP20110927?feedType=RSS&#038;feedName=Yuan&#038;virtualBrandChannel=11721&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+reuters%2FUSyuanNews+%28News+%2F+US+%2F+YUAN+GCA%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">上海地铁列车相撞，</span>270<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">多人受伤</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——高铁追尾两个月后，曾经保证不会出现这类事故的上海地铁也出现追尾事故。公众对此感到愤怒和担忧。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/09/27/the-case-of-the-disappearing-shanghai-subway-apology/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">上海地铁撞车，道歉时有时无</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——上海地铁公司在微博上的道歉，折射出社会各方对于新闻和宣传的不同态度。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/09/27/world/asia/two-tibetan-monks-set-themselves-on-fire-in-protest.html?partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">两名西藏僧人以自焚来抗议</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——四川阿坝格尔登寺的两名年轻僧人在周一自焚。其中一人是上次自焚的僧侣的兄弟。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">布鲁金斯研究所：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.brookings.edu/interviews/2011/0919_china_li.aspx?rssid=china&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+BrookingsRSS%2Ftopics%2Fchina+%28Brookings%3A+Topics+-+China%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">变化中的中国</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——对梭顿中国中心研究部主任李成的采访。他谈到中国的中产阶级对今后世界的影响，以及他们所面临的挑战</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国节奏博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.thechinabeat.org/?p=3824\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《毛的隐形之手》书评</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——即使在改革开放之后，毛泽东时代流传下来的“革命传统”依然在当今中国扮演着重要角色</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/09/26/us-china-police-microblogs-idUSTRE78P3QM20110926\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国公安部要求警方多用微博来澄清事实</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——微博越来越成为中国人获取消息的渠道，警方希望利用它来引导公众舆论</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8791105/Chinas-tax-collectors-under-fire-over-270000-yacht.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国税务部门因购买价值</span>27<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万英镑的游艇而引来批评</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——官方解释说游艇将用来在湖上收税。网民质疑按此逻辑，公安、卫生、检查等部门是否都要购买？</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110927/wl_nm/us_china_politics_zhu\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国前总理的坦率谈话搅起改革话题</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——朱�基文选中的犀利言辞很受读者欢迎，同时也反映出民间对明年领导人换届的忧虑</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>MSNBC</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://behindthewall.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2011/09/27/7995099-former-red-guard-breaks-silence-on-murder\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">一位老红卫兵打破沉默，讲述自己当年武斗杀人的经历</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span></span><span><span>60</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁的王冀豫在</span></span><span><span>40</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">多年前的武斗中杀了人，他的经历与文革中很多人都类似</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国立场博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://sinostand.com/2011/09/27/the-connection-between-language-learning-and-liberal-thinking/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">学习外语和自由派思想之间的联系</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——这位作者结合自己在中国大学里教授英语的经历，认为学习外语就是在培养不同的思维方式。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/in-china-business-travelers-take-extreme-precautions-to-avoid-cyber-espionage/2011/09/20/gIQAM6cR0K_story.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">商人到中国出差，需要加倍小心网络间谍</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——虽然美国企业中也有商业间谍，但是其规模远不如中国。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【国际外交】</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110927/ap_on_go_ca_st_pe/us_us_china\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">因美国对台售武，中国将减少与美国的军事接触</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中方在杨洁篪和希拉里的会谈后表示了这一立场。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blog.foreignpolicy.com/posts/2011/09/26/a_setback_for_the_dragon\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国在非洲遭遇挫折</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——虽然中国一直对非洲输入资金，但高调反华的候选人在赞比亚总统大选中获胜，或许传递出了一个危险的信号。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/flashpoints-blog/2011/09/27/a-trilateral-challenge/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">三边挑战</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国、巴基斯坦和印度之间的三边关系，形成了一个微妙的、往往被忽视的三角。这种关系对世界其他地区非常重要</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/sep/27/dalai-lama-banned-south-africa\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">南非反对派称，南非</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">阻止</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">达赖喇嘛到访是为了取悦中国</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——南非官方否认不让达赖出席图图主教</span></span><span><span>80</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁生日庆典是因为受到了中国压力</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业内幕》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/the-great-escape-from-the-unbearable-burden-of-credit-2011-9\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">为什么温州的企业老板纷纷欠钱逃跑？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中小企业很难从银行贷到款，不得不去借高利贷，由此引发资金危机。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">条条大路通中国：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.allroadsleadtochina.com/2011/09/23/is-chinas-economy-on-the-ledge-of-the-abyss/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国经济走向深渊？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——作者根据自己在上海的所见所闻，质疑关于中国经济发展速度减缓的说法。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《</span></span><span><span>MIT</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">技术评论》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.technologyreview.com/communications/38679/#.ToHDOEOQJcM.twitter\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">北京出租车的</span>GPS<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">数据揭示了堵车原因</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——微软亚洲研究中心的人员利用这些数据，分析出了北京堵车的热点地区以及造成堵车的原因，为城市和道路规划提供了依据</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《环球邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/asia-pacific/think-chinas-air-is-breathable-think-again/article2181489/?utm_medium=Feeds%3A%20RSS%2FAtom&#038;utm_source=Asia-Pacific&#038;utm_content=2181489\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">你认为中国的空气适合呼吸？最好再想想</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——世界卫生组织发布的大城市空气排行榜上，北京居然不是最糟糕的，这让作者十分意外。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.forbes.com/sites/kenrapoza/2011/09/27/in-china-locals-still-love-gold/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国人依然喜欢黄金</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国人对付通货膨胀的一个办法就是购买黄金。即使近来黄金价格一路下跌，他们依然对黄金情有独钟</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/09/27/the-social-ethics-of-scamming-why-am-i-always-getting-ripped-off-in-china/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">能骗就骗的社会观念：为什么我在中国总被涮？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国人卖东西的时候会根据对象不同报出不同价格。对于老外，他们报高价毫无心理负担</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《芝加哥论坛报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/chi-ap-in-purdue-researchgr,0,2419333.story\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国公司给普渡大学一千万美元拨款</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——南山铝业集团出资与普渡合作，支持其留学生计划、研究项目和教职工培训</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><i>发送邮件至 yyyyiiii+subscribe@googlegroups.com 即可订阅译文；译者的音频博客已登录iTunes，到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/id453722327?ign-mpt=uo%3D4\">这里</a>即可收听往期的译者音频节目；下载更新需翻墙。</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-1723652884839171433?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":994,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}